#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn13.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Pokkharaṇīsutta "
msgstr "2. A Lotus Pond "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn13.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.2:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, pokkharaṇī paññāsayojanāni āyāmena paññāsayojanāni vitthārena paññāsayojanāni ubbedhena, puṇṇā udakassa samatittikā kākapeyyā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose there was a lotus pond that was fifty leagues long, fifty leagues wide, and fifty leagues deep, full to the brim so a crow could drink from it. "

msgctxt "sn13.2:1.3"
msgid "Tato puriso kusaggena udakaṃ uddhareyya. "
msgstr "Then a person would pick up some water on the tip of a blade of grass. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.2:1.4"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.2:1.5"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā kusaggena udakaṃ ubbhataṃ yaṃ vā pokkharaṇiyā udakan”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the water on the tip of the blade of grass, or the water in the lotus pond?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn13.2:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ pokkharaṇiyā udakaṃ. "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the lotus pond is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.2:2.2"
msgid "Appamattakaṃ kusaggena udakaṃ ubbhataṃ. "
msgstr "The water on the tip of a blade of grass is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.2:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti pokkharaṇiyā udakaṃ upanidhāya kusaggena udakaṃ ubbhatan”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the lotus pond, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn13.2:3.1"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa abhisametāvino etadeva bahutaraṃ dukkhaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ; appamattakaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a person with comprehension, a noble disciple accomplished in view, the suffering that’s over and done with is more, what’s left is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.2:3.2"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti purimaṃ dukkhakkhandhaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya, yadidaṃ sattakkhattuṃparamatā. "
msgstr "Compared to the mass of suffering in the past that’s over and done with, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part, since there are at most seven more lives. "

msgctxt "sn13.2:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ mahatthiyo kho, bhikkhave, dhammābhisamayo; evaṃ mahatthiyo dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how very beneficial it is to comprehend the teaching and gain the vision of the teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.2:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

